answers.body_markdown:
Kotlin works with `kapt` instead of the `annotationProcessor` from the Android plugin.

You need to include and use the following in your `build.gradle` file:


    kapt {
        generateStubs = true
    }
    dependencies {
        // ...
        kapt daggerCompiler
    }

More detailed instructions can also be found here: [Dagger and Kotlin][antonioleiva]

  [antonioleiva]:https://antonioleiva.com/dagger-android-kotlin/

